<p><strong>Bug C</strong> — The shake should move the whole ship together, but right now the nose jumps around while the body stays still, so they come apart.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">pygame.draw.rect(screen, CYAN, (ship_x - 20, ship_y, 40, 50))
pygame.draw.polygon(screen, WHITE, [(ship_x + shake_x, ship_y - 20), (ship_x - 20 + shake_x, ship_y), (ship_x + 20 + shake_x, ship_y)])
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> the body does not have the shake offset added.</p>
<p><strong>Write the fixed code:</strong></p>
